{"tid":769222,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[大新聞] C朗再騷肌　射入祖記第1球","createTime":"2018-08-06T04:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T04:51:08.000Z","uid":54373,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14de1aa65ac316090aaf98ee30aa6dc0b400c08d","tid":769222,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"今個賽季最重磅的轉會，肯定是祖雲達斯以過億歐元買C朗，呢位葡萄牙球星的一舉一動都成為焦點，上周日C朗隨祖記的一場<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">訓練中</span></span>，就射入咗加盟球隊之後的首個入球，仲大騷佢嘅腿肌。<br />\n雖然祖雲達斯大部份成員正在美國出戰國際冠軍盃，但C朗等五位參加世界盃的球員則留在都靈訓練，每次訓練都吸引大批球迷圍觀，相信祖記都好耐都試過咁熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n祖記大軍周三會返到意大利進行恢復訓練，8月12日會先進行內部的家族挑戰賽，由祖雲達斯一線隊對青年軍，跟住8月18日就會出戰意甲首場聯賽。"},{"pid":"787d017314bfe70450d00ccb3c78e98d0b8404bc","tid":769222,"uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祖雲達斯一線隊對青年軍，就射入咗加盟球隊之後的首個入球，仲大騷佢嘅腿肌。</span>"},{"pid":"23c81d311c9be04147913bec9c07920e6975fcf8","tid":769222,"uid":4525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"王騎真係牙朗第一fans<br />\n永遠都跟得咁貼"},{"pid":"4cca16fe3898e73a7fc1349ee8813c8bbd087ef1","tid":769222,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23c81d311c9be04147913bec9c07920e6975fcf8","tid":769222,"uid":4525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"王騎真係牙朗第一fans<br />\n永遠都跟得咁貼"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"好勁! 對青年軍終於入到第1球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3f097c47a797924aabe0c5ea06aa947139f398","tid":769222,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cd3e7293f9f873c91209f7c7526bbca24c4597","tid":769222,"uid":46849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"p